<section class="about">

    <div class="about-card">

        <h1>About Pet Choice</h1>

        <p>

            Pet Choice is a web application developed for the WEB700 course.

            It helps users browse different cat breeds and learn about their
            personality, origin, lifespan, grooming needs, and temperament.

        </p>

        <br>

        <h2>Project Features</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>Browse over 150 cat breeds</li>

            <li>Search by breed name</li>

            <li>Search by origin</li>

            <li>Search by temperament</li>

            <li>View complete breed details</li>

            <li>REST API endpoints</li>

            <li>Responsive design using CSS</li>

        </ul>

        <br>

        <h2>Technologies Used</h2>

        <ul>

            <li>Node.js</li>

            <li>Express.js</li>

            <li>EJS</li>

            <li>HTML5</li>

            <li>CSS3</li>

            <li>JavaScript</li>

            <li>JSON Dataset</li>

        </ul>

    </div>

</section>

